-- Telekom Slovenije Full-Year Net Income Reaches 43.5 Million
-- B y   G o r d a n a   F i l i p o v i c
-- 2013-02-28T08:51:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-28/telekom-slovenije-full-year-net-income-reaches-43-5-million.html
Telekom Slovenije d.d.  reported
full-year net income of 43.5 million euros, or 28 percent more
than the previous year.  The company said its operating revenue dropped 3.8 percent
to 793.1 million euros, while operating profit declined by 1
million euros to 62.3 million euros, according to its regulatory
filing. Earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation and
amortization stood at 241.5 million euros.  To contact the reporter on this story:  Gordana Filipovic in Belgrade at 
 gfilipovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  